Specifically, `scripts/decode_canvas.js` is derived from the project's
`make_extraction/01-decode-canvas.js`. It has been modified to take input/
output paths as CLI arguments, accept both `fig-makee` and `fig-makej`
magic headers, and surface errors more cleanly. The schema decoding logic
(pako + fzstd + kiwi-schema) is unchanged.

